Falckenburg, Jakob.
[14] p.
Typis Richardi Graphei, Londini : 22 Ianuarij die mihi nigra & notabili, anno CI[C].I[C]. LXXTX [i.e. 22 Jan. 1579]
Latin verse. Imprint date contains inverted C's. Formerly pt. 2 of STC 10673--Cf. STC (2nd ed.). Reproduction of original in the Wadham College. Library.
